title: 117: The ALDI Haul Episode: September '20 Edition (Part 2)
itunes:title: The ALDI Haul Episode: September '20 Edition (Part 2)
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa, Mikey, and Jamie are sampling over a dozen healthy options from ALDI! Stuff like cauliflower rice entrées, flavored cashews, guacamole salsa, cauliflower crackers, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, crunchy finds that are meant for toddlers but perfect for adults too! So what are you waiting for? Push play now, and then head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of products mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: As promised, here’s part 2 of our major ALDI Haul! And this one is even bigger and more successful than the last one!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
